text:
TIMESHEET DAY - get everything in please! Tomorrow I will be running reports, and if your time is not in, all my numbers will be wrong, I will think we are much more wildly profitable than we are, and I will withdraw it all to fill a room and swim like Scrooge McDuck. While that sounds amazing, if you DONT put in your timesheets, and that is WRONG, then there wont be any money leftover for you. :slightly_smiling_face:

Jokes aside, this is important for the business. We have trained everyone. If you need retraining, let me know. If you need a refresher on the guidelines, let me know.

EOD today. Please. Thanks!
(clarification: time up to last week - keep this week open, no need to close out today)
